vehicles.description: White car parked on the right side of the road facing away from the ego car.
vehicles.explanation: This vehicle is stationary, but its positioning on the side of the road could narrow the driving lane for the ego car and require careful navigation to maintain a safe distance.

vehicles.description: Several parked vehicles are visible on the right side of the road, reducing the usable width of the lane.
vehicles.explanation: Parked vehicles narrow the available driving space for the ego car and could hide moving pedestrians or other hazards.

suggestions: Given the visible conditions, the ego car should proceed with caution, keeping a safe distance from the vehicle ahead and the parked car on the side. Adjust speed to ensure a safe reaction time if the road surface is indeed wet. Continuously monitor for any movement from the parked cars that could indicate a vehicle pulling into traffic.
